Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: Located at 205 Blackmarsh Road, this 2403 sf retail space is available for lease. Landlord is receptive to demising into 2 x 1200 sf units. Tenant mix includes long standing restaurant business and tax business. Surrounded by a heavy residential area and retail nodes close by including Ropewalk Lane and Columbus Drive. Easy access from Gushue extension. Ample parking onsite. Lease rate is $14.75 plus $7.50 operating costs and tenant paying own utilities.

Located at the intersection of Topsail Road and Blackmarsh Road- minutes from the new Gushue extension. This 1500 sf unit is currently a professional services office who are in place until October 31. Building has maintained long term tenants and offers an exceptional lease rate. Currently a professional services offices, this building suits retail, office and professional services. Tenant pays business tax additional to City of Mount Pearl.

Brand new building in the bustling Kenmount/Kelsey Drive area. Neighbouring Kenmount Terrace with hundreds of rooftops, seconds away from the Team Gushue Highway and next to Kelsey Drive; Kiwanis Street is a wonderful location for a number of businesses.Great plaza with exceptional curb appeal for professional offices, services and health and wellness. Found at 15 McNamara Drive, across from the Paradise Community Center and close proximity to Paradise Plaza, Walter Pennell Place offers a range of options for retail, office and professional service users. With various sizes available across three modern and bright floors, Walter Pennell Place offers the opportunity for your business to join an existing strong and diverse tenant mix-which includes bakery, pizza, fitness and office.Main floor units have direct access outside, ideal for retail or professional services. Units are ranging in size from 900 sf up to 3000 sf. All units are vanilla boxed and can be built to suit; dedicated HRV and electrical supply to all units.

Opportunity  to own your own commercial building in Clarke’s Beach with a spectacular unobstructed view of the ocean. This 7000 sf building offers a large main floor space measures approximately 3600 sf and has public washrooms, large open retail/service/restaurant space, a smaller sales area and large backroom/production/manufacturing area. Upper level boasts hardwood in 2 large open rooms plus bonus third room with plumbing hookup totaling 2050 sf. Attached warehouse/storage area off back of building adding 1100 sf to the building. Basement is not developed. A number of upgrades have transpired over the past couple of years. Option available to lease entire building for $2200/month.
